gtk-im-libthai

0.2.2 (2019-08-03)
=====
- Drop usage of deprecated GTK+ API
- Working 'make distcheck'
- XZ release tarball compression
- New configure option to disable fallback (Use with care!)

0.2.1 (2011-11-20)
=====
- Multiarch-aware installation

0.2.0 (2011-06-17)
=====
- Ported to GTK+ 3 (GTK+ 2 is still supported in the mean time)
- Fix bug with level 3 and level 5 keys

0.1.5 (2009-12-27)
=====
- Correctly fall back to rejection when client does not support correction

0.1.4 (2006-09-13)
=====
- Better support for text input when surrounding text is mixed with other 
  language
- Clean up configure and build system
- Fix compiler warnings

0.1.3 (2006-03-13)
=====

- Fix name clash when installed with gtk-im-extra.

0.1.2
=====

- Fix problem with CapsLock & NumLock (reported by Suppachoke Santiwichaya)
- Fix problem with keypad digit keys (reported by Suppachoke Santiwichaya)

